author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Capita to sell National Dental Plan to Unum Group for 31.7 mln stg
text:
Aug 10 Capita Plc
* Capita to sell National Dental Plan to Unum Group
* Has agreed sale of National Dental Plan (NDP) to Unum Group for a cash consideration of 31.7 million stg on a cash free, debt free basis Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: [CPI.L UNM.N]
